{
  "chapter": 60,
  "chapter_summary": "第60章《隋帝杨广》讲述寇仲与徐子陵在巴陵帮协助下，携带宇文阀罪证账簿入宫觐见隋帝杨广，欲借杨广之手铲除宇文化及。途中与独孤盛、虞世基、斐蕴等周旋，最终见到昏庸荒淫的杨广。杨广不务正业，只顾享乐，对军务置若罔闻，甚至欲强征民女配军士以安定军心。寇仲与徐子陵机智应对，暂时脱身，却仍被困宫中。两人夜谈心志，寇仲表明争霸天下的雄心，徐子陵则淡泊名利，兄弟情谊面临考验。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们真够运，杨广今天刚好在宫里，你们不知道吧！自从称帝后，他没有一天停息过，不是出游，就远征，搅得天怒人怨，神恼鬼愁，否则不会人人都造反了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在他将西京长安交给孙子代王杨侑，东都洛阳则由另一孙子越王杨侗管治，自己却躲到这里来，怕得连洛阳的十六院夫人都弃而不顾。那知杜伏威打到历阳来，李子通又直迫江都，天下再无他的乐土。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "代王越王，一个十二岁一个十一岁，竟要分别掌管西东两京，权柄还不是落在权臣如王世充等人手上吗？若杨广有甚么三长两短，天下会比现在乱上十倍。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "独孤峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圣上刚去了临江宫，我们要改变行程了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就叫荣华富贵了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "独孤盛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要说话！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是他们了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先把账簿给我，你们两人到偏殿等候，时机到了，本官自会来带你们去朝见圣上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "盛将军我们今趟真是得宝了，倒要看看宇文阀还能风光多久。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多点耐性好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可能我们是来错了，现在连账簿都给了人，还不知怎样才可离开。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放心吧！只要我们尚有利用价值，他们就要倚靠我们。这些人确是本末倒置，外边闹得天翻地覆不去管，一心只想斗倒身边的其他人，难怪义军声势日盛了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我最担心的就是素姐，待会见过那昏君后，我们便设法离开这里与素姐会合，立即有那么远走那么远。无论宇文阀是否被扳倒，此地都不宜久留。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说得对。宇文阀若被下旨抄家灭族，必会惹起轩然大波，宇文化及等必会全力反扑，那时江都不乱成一团才怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别忘记老爹和那李不通都在对江都虎视眈眈，只要知道江都大乱，必会挥军攻来，唉！想想都令人害怕。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位小兄弟来见过御史大人。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位小兄弟立下大功，异日本官必会奏请圣上，重重有赏。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打铁趁热，圣上该已看过账簿，现在就带两位小兄弟去晋见圣上，但千万不要提及账簿的事，就算圣上问起，你们也要装作不知有这回事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位小兄弟该是明理的人，以后好好跟随我们，包保你们荣华富贵享之不尽。来吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洛阳一天就来了三封告急文书，王世充真个混账，是否想我们给斩首呢？我把文书通通烧了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有头痛的事呢，刚才禁军统领司马德戡不理我阻止，硬闯到望江台见圣上，说甚么禁卫军粮饷被人从中剥削，士卒餐饱餐饿，兼之他们多是来自关中，知李阀起兵作反，担心家乡有事，成股成股的逃离江都，要圣上下旨安定军心呢。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好剥削军粮的人是圣上自己，我们只是代为执行，不会上身。嘻！圣上是否命人用棍将司马德戡那不识时务的家伙打出去呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知圣上是否转了死性？又或知道禁卫军中郎将窦贤亦率部下逃了，故清楚事态严重，只责成司马德戡立即把窦贤追回来，否则就要他以自己的人头作抵，真希望窦贤能走快点！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_guan",
      "speaker_name": "门官",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小民寇仲、徐子陵带到！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_guan",
      "speaker_name": "门官",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "平身！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "斐卿家来了，快助朕解决眼前这问题。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圣上，这两位……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朕知道了，其他事待会再说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圣上赐示！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朕真不明白，江都有甚么不好？南临大江，岗峦起伏，风光怡人，自古便是江淮第一胜地。偏是军士逃者日众，连窦贤都私自逃了，卿家评评是何道理？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事必是有人散播谣言，煽动军心。微臣定会查个一清二楚，报上圣上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁能煽动朕的军队，想朕南征北讨，平定天下，且三次出征高丽，军功盖世，将士敬服。朕才不信他们会听信闲言。快给朕彻查此事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那小儿为何表情古怪，竟对朕侮慢不敬。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可能是圣上本身太高深了，所以只会往深处想。我们这些简单的蚁民，想的事自然简单得多。刚刚小民就是想不透圣上高深莫测之处，所以才会皱起自己那块小脸儿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "甚么高深与简单，小子究竟意何所指？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小子想到的是若人人都能像圣上般在这里左拥右抱，仍要作逃兵的定非真正的男儿汉。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然简单！果然简单！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朕等这些做皇帝的，个个都要日埋万机，所以脑筋慢点都会祸国殃民。为今小子你说出原因，朕立即想到对策。人来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "独孤盛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "独孤盛在！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事卿家做不来的。人来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圣上赐示！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圣上赐示！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "立即派人在此处及周围徵集所有已寡之妇，待字面未嫁之女，又或尼姑女道士，适数配与朕的军士，以安定军心。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圣上！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "杨广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "够了！今天朕已花了太多时间处理国事，给朕全退下去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_guan",
      "speaker_name": "门官",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "退廷！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的事还未说，怎可以走呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "差点给你这胡乱说话的奴才害死，哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你唤我作甚么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家是自己人，何必为已过去的事争执？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的头仍在颈上，好应酬神作福，还要再多嘴逞强吗？现在本官先安排你们用休息，拣几个既标致又善解人意的宫娥来侍候你们。一有机会，我们再安排你两位去见圣上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只凭那本账簿和两位三寸不烂之舌，已足可害死宇文化及，我们两个留此尚有何作用，我们决定要走了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是一点小误会，两位小兄弟千万别意气用事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小陵说得对，我们要走了！若硬要我两兄弟留下，那就连我都不知道下趟见圣上时会说些甚么话。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_yun",
      "speaker_name": "斐蕴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "竟来威胁我们。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位小兄弟有所不知了，账簿虽给了圣上，但他何时才会翻阅，却是连圣上自己都不知道的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虞大人没告诉圣上吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然说了，但圣上却像是没听到，忙着与萧妃亲嘴狎玩，只命我们放下来，让他有闲时再看，所以我们仍要仰仗两位。嘿！听玉山说，宇文化及是你们的大仇人，大家都是同仇敌忾，不要再为这等小事介怀嘛！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎说就怎办吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好吧！不过我们只想好好休息，不用宫女来侍候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_shi_ji",
      "speaker_name": "虞世基",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完全没有问题，一切如你们所求。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "做皇帝的真懂享受。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见到杨广这样子，你还有兴趣当皇帝吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "趁此宫内长夜，可否让我寇仲表露点心声。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不准说谎！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我以前说过谎吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这至少是第二句谎话。第一句是我仲少只摸了美人儿师傅的纤纤玉手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是去问过那婆娘，老子摸了她甚么地方这种尴尬的问题吧？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "终承认曾撒谎了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些男欢女爱的事，我自然不能把细节钜细无遗的全告诉你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像从没听过仲少说过喜欢她呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算我怕了你！好！我是有点不老实，嘻！我从来就不是老实人，你陵少该比任何人都清楚。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有甚么心声须向我发表。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "话虽是那么说，但我却不是真的想做皇帝，而是想加入争霸天下这难得的游戏里。这是没有规则的游戏，在这年头仁义道德只是用口来说的，而不是用于实际的行动上。谁的势力够强，谁的拳头够硬，谁就可称王。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白你的意思，自少你就是个不甘寂寞的人，你需要的是刺激和挑战；你需要别人尊重你，讨好你。你从不怕任何人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "错了！我天不怕地不怕，但就是怕你。若你变成我的敌人，我会睡不安寝。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时你会否不择手段把我除去呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "首先是你绝不会变成我的敌人，最多是不理睬我吧！我寇仲就算能对任何人无情，但却难对你狠心。好兄弟，不要胡思乱想了，想想怎样脱身去找素姐吧！看那死胖子的神情，我们见完杨广后，步出殿门时保证每边各杀出几百名刀斧手，将我两个胡涂虫捣成肉酱。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倦死了，睡觉吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 413
    }
